data.description: Dive into coastal living in this 4BR/2BA haven, just 3 1/2 blocks from the beach! Situated on a .23 acre cul-de-sac, dead-end street  Enjoy evenings by the floor to ceiling stone wall with wood-burning fireplace in the spacious family room. Plenty of room for the family to gather in the generous kitchen with Corian countertops, a handy island, and sleek 2019 appliances. Benefit from a 2015 roof, 2018 water heater, and a 2019 electrical panel—no worries about cast iron plumbing here! 2  Car garage and the fenced backyard beckons relaxation.  Close proximity to shopping & dining, this home epitomizes the beachside dream. Paradise found!''
